title: 820-00928 Charges On All Ports, Turn On But No USB On Left Ports
message: Hello. Got this board here. It turns on, charges battery, works perfectly except for left USB ports. They can charge battery via USB-C but no USB devices get detected on them, not even get power from USB on USB mouse or any other device. The board had corrosion near U3500/5850/3906 which I cleaned and verified traces and components surrounding, but still same behavior. Where can I start?

title: 820-00928 Charges On All Ports, Turn On But No USB On Left Ports
message:
Check all components around U3500.
L3500 must get 5V, when insert and USB device into left ports.

title: 820-00928 Charges On All Ports, Turn On But No USB On Left Ports
message: U3500 was bad! I was not getting 5V on L3500. Thanks for the help!
